604
00:29:49,230 --> 00:29:50,510
I should have arrived sooner!

605
00:29:51,750 --> 00:29:52,510
It's time to move on.

606
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:54,030
Over the years,

607
00:29:54,580 --> 00:29:55,950
