627
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:03,670
Sir.

628
00:31:04,300 --> 00:31:05,030
How is Xiao Se?

629
00:31:05,860 --> 00:31:06,510
How is he?

630
00:31:09,270 --> 00:31:11,190
