636
00:31:20,580 --> 00:31:21,820
A day or two at most.

637
00:31:24,270 --> 00:31:25,060
Can anyone save him?

638
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:28,100
Qi Tianchen can save him.

639
00:31:29,100 --> 00:31:29,580
But he is back

640
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:30,510
