744
00:34:33,220 --> 00:34:34,100
I'll live.

745
00:34:35,100 --> 00:34:36,260
You speak in interesting ways.

746
00:34:41,220 --> 00:34:41,740
So...

747
00:34:42,220 --> 00:34:42,830
Miss Ruoyi.

748
00:34:43,430 --> 00:34:45,030
